    dc:description "Figure 6. Colobomatus absens sp. nov., adult female.(A) Habitus, ventral; (B) antennule, ventral; (C) buccal capsule and mouthparts, ventral; (D) leg 1, ventrolateral; (E) tip of thoracic process, ventral. Abbreviations: A, antenna; la, labium; mx, maxillule; Mx, maxilla; Mxp, maxilliped." ;
